<item>
            <title>[SOLR-16861] Coordinator node does not have the correct collection/core in MDCLoggingContext</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16861</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In Coordinator node, the MDCLoggingContext has the synthetic core info set while processing core requests, therefore log prints collection/shard/replica of the synthetic collection/core info.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should instead have the collection it queries on set.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
